data.description: Welcome home to this Charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home located on a quiet cul-de-sac in Heritage Park. This home would be perfect for a first time home buyer or if you are just simply looking to downsize for a low up keep this is the house for you! Some of the upgrades done on the home include granite counter tops, new roof 2018, new double pane windows, dishwasher, digital water heater with 12 year warranty, garage door opener. Home has been wired to be a smart home with Echo, mounted Tv in garage conveys. The backyard is a Gardener's Paradise with over 100 different Native Plants and Flowers which attract Hummingbirds and Butterflies in the spring time. Great storage shed located in the back. Zoned to CCISD quick commute to I45 and close proximity to plenty of dining restaurants and shopping for entertaining family and friends. Schedule your appointment today!
